last_episode_to_air.overview: Gerry and Yvonne host a group game night. Agent Foster meets a person from her past. Walsh, Jeff, Don, and Kurt enact their mutiny against Eric.

name: People of Earth
overview: Skeptical journalist Ozzie Graham investigates a support group for alien abductees to write about the members' supposed encounters. The more he digs into their oddball claims, the more he realizes there is truth in their stories and possibly even signs that point to his own alien abduction.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: In Season Two, onetime outsider Ozzie Graham finds himself part of this eclectic group of misfits—all the while struggling with the knowledge that life exists beyond our world. Meanwhile, Special Agent Alex Foster, a smart, dedicated FBI investigator has come to Beacon on the hunt for local newspaper owner Jonathan Walsh for white collar crime, but soon learns he harbors even greater secrets.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: Things get weird for New York journalist Ozzie Graham after a suspicious car accident sends him searching for answers at StarCrossed, a support group for alien “experiencers.”

episodes.name: Sponsored By
episodes.overview: Trying to win over Ozzie, Gerry goes above and beyond what a good sponsor would do. Chelsea opens up to Father Doug about her marriage. Tensions run high as Jeff, Don and Kurt prepare for the alien invasion.

episodes.name: Acceptance
episodes.overview: Ozzie helps Richard face his broken marriage. Yvonne and Gerry investigate a mysterious cover up; Jonathan Walsh delivers some upsetting news to Jeff and Don.

episodes.name: Past, Present and Future
episodes.overview: Ozzie's former boss, Jonathan Walsh, makes a surprising visit to Beacon; the origin of StarCrossed is revealed as Gina takes a trip down memory lane.

episodes.name: Unexplained
episodes.overview: Unexplainable visions and hallucinations have Ozzie thinking heÂs losing his mind. Chelsea and Father Doug connect over Bible Study. Kelly continues to struggle with relationships.

episodes.name: Significant Other
episodes.overview: Ozzie and Father Doug have a night out. Gina holds a coming out event for the members of StarCrossed. Jeff makes a connection with a stranger in an online chat room.

episodes.name: Last Day on Earth
episodes.overview: Gerry says goodbye to StarCrossed as he readies for his own long-awaited experience. Jonathan Walsh shares game changing information with Ozzie. Don and Kelly go on a date.

episodes.name: Mars or Bust
episodes.overview: Ozzie makes a surprising confession during an interview. Father Doug has an experience; Jeff is determined to find Kurt's killer.

episodes.name: Lost and Found
episodes.overview: Ozzie leaves Beacon hoping to return to a normal life. Chelsea goes on the road with Operation Mongoose. The members of StarCrossed contemplate an uncertain future.

episodes.name: Snake Man and Little Guy
episodes.overview: Ozzie has a significant breakthrough. Jeff and Jonathan Walsh square off before the impending invasion. The members of StarCrossed struggle to find meaning after the group's break-up.

episodes.name: New Beginnings
episodes.overview: After learning the members of StarCrossed were on the ship as kids, Ozzie tries to get the group together. FBI agent Foster is sent to Beacon to investigate Jonathan Walsh. A merger takes place on the ship & the aliens are under new management.

episodes.name: Uneasy Alliance
episodes.overview: Agent Foster continues her investigation into Walsh by meeting with StarCrossed. Yvonne leads a small team to search for Gerry -- unaware he's been abducted. Meanwhile, on the ship, Jeff asks Gerry for advice on how to deal with his new boss.

episodes.name: Gerry's Return
episodes.overview: Gerry returns to Earth but Yvonne has a rule about not dating other experiencers, putting their romantic relationship in jeopardy. Father Doug and Chelsea go on their first real date. Ozzie and Agent Foster make contact with Jonathan Walsh.

episodes.name: Always a Day Away
episodes.overview: Gina uses her birthday party to distract Agent Foster so that Ozzie can sneak out to meet Walsh. The Cube pressures Jeff to clean up the ship. Don wants to tell Kelly a secret. Father Doug and Chelsea find it's hard to get out of their previous commitments.

episodes.name: Why Can't We Be Friends?
episodes.overview: Ozzie confronts Walsh about being an alien. Richard gets fired from his job and joins Agent Foster on her search for Walsh.

episodes.name: Aftermath
episodes.overview: The group copes with a tragedy. Agent Foster reports back to the FBI. Jonathan Walsh and Don have reservations about the alien mission.

episodes.name: Bee Kind
episodes.overview: The group asks Agent Foster for help with an investigation. Chelsea and her husband go to marriage counseling. Jeff blames Don for bringing an intruder onto the ship.

episodes.name: Alien Experiencer Expo
episodes.overview: The group attends an alien experiencer convention. Gina meets one of her therapy heroes. Gerry & Yvonne have their first fight. Richard tries to prove to Agent Foster that aliens do exist. Both Chelsea and Agent Foster receive unexpected news.

episodes.name: Truth or Dare
episodes.overview: Agent Foster goes to Gina with a personal problem. Richard sues his employer for wrongful termination with the help of the group as character witnesses. Jeff is blackmailed by Eric and Jonathan Walsh offers his support.

episodes.name: Game Night
episodes.overview: Gerry and Yvonne host a group game night. Agent Foster meets a person from her past. Walsh, Jeff, Don, and Kurt enact their mutiny against Eric.
